{"tid":1824631,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"工廈HKBN焗加價，強行100mm轉500mb","createTime":"2020-01-14T14:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T15:59:33.000Z","uid":71168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4f7c8e414b15785142dff66d339089dd9067b660","tid":1824631,"uid":71168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T14:59:02.000Z","msg":"唔係想轉plan，Sales可以出返去。棟大廈得HKBN，所以冇得轉。<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇巴打試過呢個情況？<br />\n佢話成棟大廈轉咗做500mb，所以焗我加價，$188加到$318。我本身需求不大，100mb夠用，覺得$188已經好貴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我話唔要500mb得唔得，佢話唔得。簽咗兩年約，有乜理由話加就加？<br />\n而家日日打過嚟叫我簽畀佢，有乜解救？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc83a62d91a26f2570199b68bc1c5e19cc2c0c6","tid":1824631,"uid":224743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T14:59:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"015236705e9f44a0cfd946fb6adce481b69fa0ac","tid":1824631,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:00:35.000Z","msg":"認真，cut"},{"pid":"de17de50ce955ed21b6639849315c55a0ec8bb48","tid":1824631,"uid":153722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:02:17.000Z","msg":"咁你咪唔好用囉"},{"pid":"02e78a851df499d4f9566f5aa067d6adc3f0206f","tid":1824631,"uid":71168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"015236705e9f44a0cfd946fb6adce481b69fa0ac","tid":1824631,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:00:35.000Z","msg":"認真，cut"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:05:01.000Z","msg":"有部imac喺到，主要剪片，少量上網。用手機Wi-Fi會唔會好笨？"},{"pid":"c78927fed38af12265dc72d8f536a9841ed3a2eb","tid":1824631,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02e78a851df499d4f9566f5aa067d6adc3f0206f","tid":1824631,"uid":71168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"015236705e9f44a0cfd946fb6adce481b69fa0ac","tid":1824631,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:00:35.000Z","msg":"認真，cut"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:05:01.000Z","msg":"有部imac喺到，主要剪片，少量上網。用手機Wi-Fi會唔會好笨？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:11:09.000Z","msg":"手機無限嘅，就用手機wifi <br />\n最撚憎局鳩人續約<br />\n早前又係有HKBN打嚟話要升級，原本$168/月 100mb，話要升500mb，要$200幾<br />\n我：咁到期我會cut約<br />\n即刻平多我幾十/月，最後我都係話會cut，然後收線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69295b36a53433801765545ab2ee20ecea7f6a54","tid":1824631,"uid":297493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T17:18:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eaeb3e4ed0d7e46f322572391fa0d11b0a7017f1","tid":1824631,"uid":342056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T20:47:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce199fc1235898d917b16dfa390ad80ebeb910bf","tid":1824631,"uid":221369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T20:48:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1b4769835c9f40b86b6dcf8d3b542afad0ef035","tid":1824631,"uid":342056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T20:48:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca1a621152fd2154444983b8d9102909e3973d63","tid":1824631,"uid":270986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T05:18:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b7455fd1e9693464841e9d3d95686b6b2a0d697","tid":1824631,"uid":278706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:09:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7ebd0da239fdc01a7c8be0cb79c24aa26035a94","tid":1824631,"uid":317891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:59:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}